{"tid":1286870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南華早報：傳「中國」要確認「美國」鬆綁華為禁令，才願買農產品","createTime":"2019-07-05T03:50:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T07:17:16.000Z","uid":134071,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2474b442f48cf7e0f41880ad3f8aad3ace3c3eba","tid":1286870,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:50:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2019/07/05/china-usa-huawei-agricultural-products/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2019%2F07%2F05%2Fchina-usa-huawei-agricultural-products%2F&d=J%2B7a%2FypYnyyex2M81OHxVZMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=176c89b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2019/07/05/china-usa-huawei-agricultural-products/</a><br />\n<br />\n南華早報：傳中國要確認美國鬆綁華為禁令，才願買農產品<br />\nJuly 5, 2019 by MoneyDJ<br />\n<br />\n中美下週將恢復貿易談判，據了解，北京要先確定川普政府真的鬆綁華為禁令，才會購買美國農產品，倘若雙方無法解決此一問題，談判可能立刻破局，美國將對中國開徵新一波關稅。<br />\n<br />\n南華早報報導，內情人士向該報表示，美國代表下週將出訪北京，進行貿易磋商。談判順利與否，很大一部分取決於美國如何處理華為禁令。上週末川習會上，川普宣布美國企業可以恢復供貨華為，中方則允諾要大量購買美國農產品。但是外界對川習兩人實際同意的內容莫衷一是，放寬華為禁令更出現許多雜音。<br />\n<br />\n美國消息人士說，北京對於立刻恢復購買美國黃豆含糊其辭，要先確定川普兌現承諾，下令放寬華為禁令後，才會出手。他說，未來幾天白宮或許會宣布，美企在何種情況下，可以恢復供貨華為。要是磋商代表無法解決這些問題，談判可能觸礁，美國將對剩餘未課稅的 3,000 億美元中國商品，開徵關稅。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，美國政府仍在討論如何鬆綁禁令，華為禁售令的寬限期 8 月 13 日到期，美方考慮延長、或是設立特別審核程序。熟知北京政府看法的人士說，儘判障礙重重，中方仍對前景審慎樂觀。<br />\n<br />\n川普宣布鬆綁華為，實際上禁令並未解除。路透社報導，美國商務部 3 日表示，華為仍在黑名單上，商務部以「最高國安審查規格」（the highest national security scrutiny），處理美企申請出口華為的事宜。"},{"pid":"4d39af00ff4702a4cc4bdaf8cbf5fa09f31e89f0","tid":1286870,"uid":134071,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:52:57.000Z","msg":"咁好難有deal了?"},{"pid":"4a69cdcfaf5f8c84217deb1dd11e2e0931d7d30e","tid":1286870,"uid":14918,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:53:23.000Z","msg":"中共無左華為 = 無左對眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9508785752d11ab83f5ba1a960fbc0a34be5144","tid":1286870,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:53:34.000Z","msg":"識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d6a780f70cf49dec83735078d625fb39322cc05","tid":1286870,"uid":122604,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:55:26.000Z","msg":"證明華為對支那好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cf5ec97e9c951e216516cd59ed14ed5f30007ad","tid":1286870,"uid":50386,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:58:34.000Z","msg":"主客都未識分學人講條件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3cd5701ce08b1b7ec2cd10a729cc3e0b5d9159d","tid":1286870,"uid":26752,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"9cf5ec97e9c951e216516cd59ed14ed5f30007ad","tid":1286870,"uid":50386,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:58:34.000Z","msg":"主客都未識分學人講條件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:02:43.000Z","msg":"傳「美國」要確認「支那」買農產品，才願鬆綁華為禁令<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"633bd1346bd82f790b8f42e66451618ddcd413de","tid":1286870,"uid":1989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:03:16.000Z","msg":"Ok咁你唔使買了<br />\n請返屋企自己含撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27af80c9da97aab5aab95f96e46ddaa242af85f9","tid":1286870,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:04:13.000Z","msg":"一個維穩費高過軍費嘅國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當人民係敵人多過外面敵對國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e95d4dd31ad70cd4316413e4817c9fdc16319767","tid":1286870,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:04:17.000Z","msg":"同自己個肚鬥氣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c95d3e392745f96293086a0359d5547ff5d4f81f","